title: PUBLIC NOTICE The State of Oregon will be conducting a
text:
PUBLIC NOTICE The State of Oregon will be conducting a ad date: 10/03/2015 
PUBLIC NOTICE The State of Oregon will be conducting a public meeting to solicit Public Comment on Phase TWO of the States Application for a Housing and Urban Development (HUD) National Disaster Resilience Competition Grant. The meeting will be hosted by the Department of Administrative Services at the Executive Office Building, located at 155 Cottage Street NE in Salem, Oregon with satellite venues at the Brookings, Oregon, City Hall Council Chambers, 898 Elk Drive and Reedsport, Oregon, City Hall Conference Room, 451 Winchester Avenue. The meeting will occur on Monday, October 5, 2015 at 10:00 am. Individuals wishing to provide public comment or requiring Americans with Disabilities (ADA) accommodation should contact Yumei Wang at: Yumei.q.wang@oregon.gov (please put "ADA Assistance/Public Comment" in the subject line) before Friday, October 2, 2015. Publish September 26 & October 3, 2015 No. 71109960
